    "QuantumMob/Q3", "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "GHZState[{s1, s2, ..., sn}, k] returns the (k + 1) thgeneralized \
Greenberger-Horne-Zeilinger (GHZ) state for species {s1, s2, ...}. All \
species are assumed to have the same Hilbert space dimension. GHZState[{s1, \
s2, ..., sn}, {k1, k2, ...}] returns a list of k_i^th GHZ states. \
GHZState[{s1, s2, ..., sn}, All] returns a list of all GHZ states. \
GHZState[{s1, s2, ..., sn}] is equivalent to GHZState[{s1, s2, ..., sn}, 0]. \
GHZState[{d, n}, spec] consider n d-level unlabeled systems.", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "GHZState", 
